general.desc: DFNN Inc is an information technology solutions provider and systems integrator. The firm engages in the provision of information technology services to financial institutions and gaming companies. It also develops, operates, and maintains web-based and wireless applications for financial institutions and gaming companies. The company also provides proprietary order routing software technology and web-advertising services to stock brokerage firms. It earns maximum revenue from Software Solutions.
